org.hibernate.sql.ast.tree.expression

Class AbstractLiteral<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.sql.ast.tree.expression.AbstractLiteral<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.hibernate.query.sqm.sql.internal.DomainResultProducer<T>, SqlSelectionProducer, Expression, SqlAstNode, JdbcParameterBinder

    public abstract class AbstractLiteral<T>
extends Object
implements JdbcParameterBinder, Expression, org.hibernate.query.sqm.sql.internal.DomainResultProducer<T>
    We classify literals different based on their source so that we can handle then differently when rendering SQL. This class offers convenience for those implementations

    Can function as a ParameterBinder for cases where we want to treat literals using bind parameters.
